 The royal family were not left out in celebrating Father’s Day on Sunday, June 16. Duchess Meghan Markle and Prince Harry’s official Instagram account shared a photo of their son, Archie Harrison Mountbatten-Windsor. The photo marks the first time they have shown the face of the little royal baby. The caption for the post, which honored Prince Harry on his first Father’s Day, read: “Happy Father’s Day! And wishing a very special first Father’s Day to The Duke of Sussex. Prince Archie was born on May 6 and was introduced to the world on May 8. See the adorable photo below: Prince Archie Harrison Mountbatten-Windsor | Photo: Instagram/SussexRoyal